The '''B'ay tribe''' was a tribe of scavenging [[Jawa/Legends|Jawas]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. The clan owned three [[Sandcrawler/Legends|sandcrawlers]].

==History==
Around [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]], the clan was wiped out by a surviving [[Dark Trooper/Legends|dark trooper]] on a Rebel ship they were scavenging. The sandcrawler in use went hurling out of control and was destroyed when it went off into the [[Mos Espa/Legends|Mos Espa]] [[Mos Espa Grand Arena/Legends|Arena]], nearly killing the mercenaries [[Spiker]], [[Gizman|Big Gizz]], and [[Onoh]] who had an encampment near by. Only one member, [[Klepti B'ay|Klepti]], survived, swearing a [[Life debt/Legends|life debt]] to the three mercenaries.

